<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <link href="../public/stylesheets/login2.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../public/stylesheets/menuu.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="/javascripts/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
    <meta charset="utfF-8">
    <title>MakSse Login</title>
    <script>
        $(function(){


            $("#btnJoin").click(
                    function(){
                        if($("#id").val() == "")
                        {
                            alert("아이디를 꼭 입력 하세요");
                            $("#id").focus();
                            return ;
                        }

                        if($("#passwd").val() == "")
                        {
                            alert("비밀번호를 꼭 입력 하세요");
                            $("#passwd").focus();
                            return ;
                        }


                        $("#login").submit();

                    }
            );

        });
    </script>
</head>

<body>
<h1>
    <a href="#"><img src="../public/images/logo1.JPG" alt="logo-image" ></a>
</h1>
<div class="header-bar"></div>
<div id="main">

    <div class="login-1"><!--logo이미지 클릭하면 메인홈으로 간다.-->
        <div class="login-2"><!--페이스북, 카카오, 네이버를 이용한 로그인 클릭하면 계정연결-->
            <ul>

                <li>
                    <div class="facebook-login">
                        <a href="#"><img src="../public/images/페이스북1.JPG" alt="logo" width="10">
                            <p>페이스북계정으로 시작하기</p></a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="kakao-login">
                        <a href="#"><img src="../public/images/kakaologin1.JPG" alt="kakaologo" width="10">
                            <p>카카오계정으로 시작하기</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <div class="naver-login">
                        <a href="#"><img src="../public/images/naverlogin1.JPG" alt="naverlogo" width="10">
                            <p>네이버계정으로 시작하기</p>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <form id="login" action="/test" method = "post">
            <div class="login-1-t">로그인</div>

            <h2 class="login-box">
                <a href="#"><button class="login-button" id="btnjoin"  align="center"  ><p>로그인</p></button></a>
                <p><input type="text" style="width:250px; height:50px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                          name="id"  id="id"  placeholder="이메일(아이디)"><br>
                    <input type="password" style="width:250px; height:50px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                           name="password"  id="password" placeholder="비밀번호"><br>
                    자동 로그인<input type="checkbox" style="margin-top:10px; width:25px; height:25px; font-size:22px;"
                                 name="자동로그인" value="#" >
                    아이디 저장<input type="checkbox" style="width:25px; height:25px; font-size:22px;"
                                 name="아이디저장" value="#" >
                    <a href="#"> 아이디/비밀번호 찾기</a>


                </p>
            </h2>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="join">
        <div class="join-box-1"><a href="#main" alt="회원가입북마크">회원가입</a></div>
        <div class="join-box">
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td><input type="text" style="width:190px; height:30px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                               name="이름" placeholder="이름"></td>
                    <td><input type="text" style="width:190px; height:30px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                               name="닉네임" placeholder="닉네임"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2"><input type="text" style="width:390px; height:30px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                                           name="id" placeholder="이메일(아이디)"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2"><input type="password" style="width:390px; height:30px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                                           name="비밀번호" placeholder="비밀번호"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2"><input type="password" style="width:390px; height:30px; font-size:22px; font-family: sans-serif;"
                                           name="비밀번호확인" placeholder="비밀번호 확인"></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2">
                        <a  href="/rule"><div class="join-button" align="center"><p>회원가입</p></div></a>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="join-notice">
            <p> 막시피와 함께 맛있는 레시피를 공유해주세요:)!</p>
            <br>
            <br/>
            <br>
            <br/>
            <br>
            <br/>
            <br>
            <br/>
            <p> 막시피를 떠나실려고요? :(</p>
            <a  href="#"><div class="join-button" align="center"><p>회원 탈퇴</p></div></a>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
